pull_request.title: Bump gitpython from 3.0.7 to 3.1.30 in /scripts/copy_from_upstream
pull_request.body:
Bumps [gitpython](https://github.com/gitpython-developers/GitPython) from 3.0.7 to 3.1.30.
Release notes

Sourced from gitpython's releases.

v3.1.30 - with important security fixes

See gitpython-developers/GitPython#1515 for details.

3.1.20

No release notes provided.

Commits
  • 141cd65 adjust changelog prior to release
  • 678a8fe Merge pull request #1521 from stsewd/block-insecure-options
  • ae6a6e4 Fix type hint on create_tag
  • 5bce9b4 Document PushInfoList
  • f4f2658 Updates from review
  • 9dc4392 Submodule tests
  • c8ae33b More tests
  • b92f01a Update/add tests for Repo.clone*
  • fd2c6da Updates from review
  • e6108c7 Block unsafe options and protocols by default
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
